$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Terasic DE10-Lite out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Seven-seg: decoded readout — counter / accelerometer axes (all digits live). Buttons: staggered presses.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! ledr0 $end
$var wire 1 " ledr1 $end
$var wire 1 # ledr2 $end
$var wire 1 $ ledr3 $end
$var wire 1 % ledr4 $end
$var wire 1 & ledr5 $end
$var wire 1 ' ledr6 $end
$var wire 1 ( ledr7 $end
$var wire 1 ) ledr8 $end
$var wire 1 * ledr9 $end
$var wire 1 + sw0 $end
$var wire 1 , sw1 $end
$var wire 1 - sw2 $end
$var wire 1 . sw3 $end
$var wire 1 / sw4 $end
$var wire 1 0 sw5 $end
$var wire 1 1 sw6 $end
$var wire 1 2 sw7 $end
$var wire 1 3 sw8 $end
$var wire 1 4 sw9 $end
$var wire 1 5 key0 $end
$var wire 1 6 key1 $end
$var wire 4 7 hex0 $end
$var wire 4 8 hex1 $end
$var wire 4 9 hex2 $end
$var wire 4 : hex3 $end
$var wire 4 ; hex4 $end
$var wire 4 < hex5 $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
